OL,3,CHealth minister urges junior doctors
OL,4,Cto cancel strike
OL,6,FThe health minister has pleaded with
OL,7,Fjunior doctors in Northern Ireland not
OL,8,Fto strike next month, warning that the
OL,9,Fwalkout would impact heavily on
OL,10,Fpatients.
OL,12,FIn a letter to the BMA, Robin Swann
OL,13,Fsaid he intends to increase junior
OL,14,Fdoctors' pay by up to 10.7%.
OL,16,FHowever, he said that is the very
OL,17,Flimit of what can be afforded at this
OL,18,Fpoint.
