OL,3,CHealth minister urges junior doctors
OL,4,Cto cancel strike
OL,6,F"Negotiation is about the art of the
OL,7,Fpossible. While I fully understand the
OL,8,Fanger of junior doctors who have seen
OL,9,Fpay not keep pace with inflation in
OL,10,Frecent years, it is not realistic to
OL,11,Fexpect this issue to be resolved by
OL,12,Fthe Executive and Assembly at this
OL,13,Fpoint in time.
OL,15,F"Pay erosion has been a consequence of
OL,16,FUK Government fiscal policies over the
OL,17,Fpast decade and has been experienced
OL,18,Facross the UK public sector. This is a
OL,19,Fnational issue.
